miPhysics.Engine

Class PhyModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • miPhysics.Engine.Module
      • miPhysics.Engine.PhyObject
        • miPhysics.Engine.PhyModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    miString, miTopoCreator

    public class PhyModel
extends PhyObject
    Main class for physical model objects. A model may contain masses, interactions and sub-models.
